                <td bgcolor="#f0f0f0" width="20%" valign="top"><b>Release Notes:</b></td>
                <td id="customfield_11841-267951-value" class="value" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="80%">      <p>Added LVI (lymphvascularinvasion) from OpenClinica for patients diagnosed 2024+. See posit report for changes - no other variables dealt with in the primary site surgery function were impacted by this change except surgery_lymphovascular_invasion, which was directly affected by this addition (used lymphvascularinvasion from both OC and registry): <a href="https://posit-connect.prod.aws.npowermedicine.com/connect/#/apps/c19b6826-b20b-46d0-9609-1f472389bba9" title="smart-link" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer">https://posit-connect.prod.aws.npowermedicine.com/connect/#/apps/c19b6826-b20b-46d0-9609-1f472389bba9</a> </p>
  </td>
